OL,3,CVandalism forces buses to stop calling
OL,4,Cat station
OL,6,FBusses will stop calling at a station
OL,7,Fin Dumfries and Galloway due to
OL,8,Fvandalism.
OL,10,FIt's after the windows of two vehicles
OL,11,Fwere smashed when they were parked up
OL,12,Fat Annan Bus Station.
OL,14,FStagecoach has now confirmed that the
OL,15,F79 and 179 services will no longer be
OL,16,Fcalling at the station.
OL,18,FThe operator says it has taken the
OL,19,Fdecision following "repeated
OL,20,Finstances" of vandalism over the past
OL,21,Fyear.
