OL,3,CVandalism forces buses to stop calling
OL,4,Cat station
OL,6,FStagecoach has said that despite
OL,7,Fraising issues over the behaviour of
OL,8,Fsome people at Annan Bus Station with
OL,9,FPolice Scotland, the situation hasn't
OL,10,Fimproved.
OL,12,FIn a statement it said: "We can
OL,13,Fconfirm that two of our buses were
OL,14,Fvandalised while parked at Annan Bus
OL,15,FStation on Tuesday evening, with
OL,16,Fwindows smashed in separate incidents.
OL,18,F"Both matters have been reported to
OL,19,FPolice Scotland and we are continuing
OL,20,Fto engage with them to seek urgent
OL,21,Faction.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
