OL,3,CVandalism forces buses to stop calling
OL,4,Cat station
OL,6,F"Sadly these are not isolated events.
OL,7,FOver the past year, there have been
OL,8,Frepeated instances of vandalism and
OL,9,Fanti-social behaviour in and around
OL,10,FAnnan Bus Station. Despite our ongoing
OL,11,Fdialogue with Police Scotland, the
OL,12,Fsituation has not improved.
OL,14,F"The safety of our employees and
OL,15,Fcustomers must come first, and we have
OL,16,Ftherefore taken the difficult decision
OL,17,Fto temporarily suspend use of the bus
OL,18,Fstation until we can be assured it is
OL,19,Fsafe to operate."
