OL,3,CVandalism forces buses to stop calling
OL,4,Cat station
OL,6,FStagecoach has also said that it is
OL,7,Furging local people to contact
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway Council to help
OL,9,Fbring positive change.
OL,11,FThey said: "We're fully prepared to
OL,12,Fwork with Police Scotland and local
OL,13,Fauthorities to find a lasting solution
OL,14,Fto this ongoing issue.
OL,16,F"We would also urge local residents
OL,17,Fand businesses to raise their concerns
OL,18,Fdirectly with the council to help
OL,19,Fbring about real, tangible change that
OL,20,Fmakes Annan Bus Station a safe and
OL,21,Fwelcoming environment for everyone.
