OL,4,Cat station
OL,6,F"Customers can continue to board and
OL,7,Falight at nearby alternative stops on
OL,8,FScott's Street and High Street.
OL,9,FService updates will be provided on
OL,10,Four website, app and social media
OL,11,Fchannels."
OL,13,FPolice Scotland says it is looking to
OL,14,Fwork with various local groups to
OL,15,Freduce anti-social behaviour.
