OL,6,FIn a statement Chief Inspector Duncan
OL,7,FCameron said: "We are committed to
OL,8,Freducing anti-social behaviour and we
OL,9,Fwork collaboratively with a range of
OL,10,Flocal partners to reduce, prevent and
OL,11,Faddress such behaviour.
OL,13,F"When necessary, the appropriate
OL,14,Faction will be taken when incidents
OL,15,Fare reported and offenders are
OL,16,Fidentified.
